    <h1>Influencer Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Partnering with individuals who have a <strong>trusted, engaged following</strong> to promote your brand to their audience. A $21.1 billion industry in 2023 — and 89% of marketers say the ROI matches or beats other channels.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
