            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Nano-influencers: $50–$500 per post (or gifting only). Micro-influencers: $500–$5,000. Macro-influencers: $5,000–$25,000. Mega-influencers and celebrities: $25,000+. Pricing varies significantly by platform and industry niche.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
