            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, but on different platforms. LinkedIn partnerships with industry analysts, respected consultants, and niche practitioners generate strong trust and authority similar to B2C lifestyle creator relationships.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
