              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Track impressions, engagement rate, referral traffic via UTM links, promo code redemptions, and conversions. Focus on cost per acquisition rather than vanity metrics like follower count or raw impressions.</p></div></div>
